    }

</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;After completing his studies at Ateneo, José Rizal enrolled at the University of Santo Tomas in 1878 to study Philosophy and Letters, inspired by his interest in the humanities and European philosophy. However, by 1879, he shifted to Medicine, driven by the desire to treat his mother, Teodora Alonso, who was losing her eyesight.        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Despite excelling academically, Rizal grew disillusioned with the racial discrimination he faced from the Spanish friars who dominated the university. This prejudice ultimately motivated him to seek education abroad, where he believed he could study more freely and without bias.        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
    </property>
   </widget>
